        "Description": "Good day, 47.\r\rWe have been tasked with cleaning up the Creek - specifically by Richard Wilson. The couple moved to town for a fresh start after Susan&apos;s constant cheating, and the husband has been too scared to confront his wife head-on. After learning his wife has already found a new lover in the form of a server boy alongside bringing their bodyguard in the move -Susan&apos;s former lover who she claimed to have been done with- Richard has determined to provide a more permenant divorce notice.",
